dto
Class MarketDataDTO

java.lang.Object
  dto.MarketDataDTO

public class MarketDataDTO
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to contain data elements that capture the values that make up the current market. This will be used throughout the trading system so a DTO is used to facilitate more efficient data transfer between objects.

Author:
Urvi
